    "src_002 (collection 4237104) was correctly recognized as a SECOND derivative index into the same underlying kirkebok rather than an independent source — two indexes of one register confirm transcription fidelity, not the underlying fact twice.",
    "FAN item (pli_007/src_004) is well-targeted: daughter Marthe Marie Grude f. Birkeland in Stavanger 1891 corroborates family's continued Stavanger residence and, indirectly, the burial location."
  ],
  "must_address": [
