      "specific_action": "Open the Stavanger Domkirke burial register for late December 1883 directly on digitalarkivet.no, locate the Christian Frederik Birkeland entry, and transcribe the full original. If unretrievable, document the access attempt explicitly in a log entry and proceed to exhaustiveness declaration noting the documented limitation."
    }
